      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/intesa-targets-new-digital-only-clients-after-antritrust-blow-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利最大的联合圣保罗银行周五表示，在一项反垄断决定有效地阻止了现有客户的迁移后，该银行已通过其纯数字业务部门 Isybank 获得了约 90,000 名新客户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/intesa-targets-new-digital-only-clients-after-antritrust-blow-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 14:43:36 GMT</pubDate>
